{"type": "article", "id": 27377, "title": "满月台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-27T06:53:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132210Pp9Mq0Whlc6ArfFo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>古时人们常以圆月来寄托思乡之情，由设计师黄国栋创立的的<a href=\"http://ey-products.com/\">意外设计</a>以此为灵感推出了这款名为满月的台灯。外壳采用榉木制作，内置的 LED 灯从中间透出温暖的光线，内侧面还添加了一个可插入植物的小孔，在枝叶的搭配下看起来更诗情画意。这是它的<a href=\"http://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1.w6048809-4031259655.6.8zAHVl&amp;id=35208151201\">购买链接</a>，售价为 498 元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021322084aG2sMOkIQVmZoiA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132209tkVXsSKA7jIOv4G5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132209tZxzgM0iOuPc8l5T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132210nzL6S15Pfs9U2xhX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}